Revision history for Perl extension modules.

0.01  Wed Mar 20 12:20:07 2002
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
		-A -X -a -n modules

0.02 03-22-2002 15:55

	- Added checking for eval-errors

	'Jesse Porter' pointed me to include it.

0.03 25.06.2002 13:48

	- Added option 'force'. It is turned ON by default. It
	controls if 'modules' tries to catch locally-not-loadable
	modules from CPAN via the CPAN module.

	- Module arguments are now passable via a hashref. Have
	a look on example 2 in the pod.
